---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<div class="bg-dark-800 rounded-xl p-5 shadow-lg border border-white/5 mt-4 group hover:border-primary-500/30 transition-colors">
  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-3 text-primary-400 font-bold border-l-4 border-primary-500 pl-3">
    <Icon name="ri:megaphone-line" />
    <span>公告</span>
  </div>
  
  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4">
    欢迎来到秋兰以为佩的博客！这里记录技术思考与生活感悟。
    <br/>
    <span class="text-xs opacity-70 mt-2 block">--- 2025.12.18</span>
  </p>
  
  <button class="w-full py-2 bg-dark-700 hover:bg-primary-600 hover:text-white text-gray-300 text-sm rounded-lg transition-colors flex items-center justify-center gap-2">
    <span>了解更多</span>
    <Icon name="ri:arrow-right-line" />
  </button>
</div>
